F(C)=a\cos C+b\sin C
F'(C)=-a\sin C+b\cos C
F, F'(C)=0\implies a\sin C-b\cos C=0\iff \frac a{\cos C}=\frac b{\sin C}=\pm \sqrt{a^2+b^2}
F''(C)=-a\cos C-b\sin C
\frac a{\cos C}=\frac b{\sin C}=\sqrt{a^2+b^2}, F''(C)=-\sqrt{a^2+b^2}<0
F_{max}=\sqrt{a^2+b^2}
